SUMMARY:Iyengar Yoga
DESCRIPTION:Join Debbie Bartholomew for Iyengar Yoga classes in Todmorden! Whatever your experience or ability come along to class and learn the art of Iyengar Yoga in a fun and relaxed environment. \n\n\n\nIyengar Yoga is a long established approach which helps students to build confidence\, fitness and wellbeing.  In class we focus on alignment\, precision\, extension and breath which helps improve the sense of ease in mind and body. \n\n\n\nDebbie is an extremely knowledgable teacher with over 30 years experience.  She holds the level 3 Iyengar teaching qualification and the worldwide Iyengar Yoga certification mark which assures quality and excellence in teaching. \n\n\n\nTo book please use the contact infromation below:
URL:https://tlchub.org.uk/event/iyengar-yoga/2026-04-01/
LOCATION:Todmorden Learning Centre and Community Hub\, Todmorden Learning Centre and Community Hub\, Burnley Rd\, Todmorden\, OL14 7BX\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:Sport and exercise
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://usercontent.one/wp/tlchub.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/debbie-yoga-1.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Debbie Bartholomew":MAILTO:debbieyoga@yahoo.com
END:VEVENT
