SUMMARY:Life Drawing Wednesdays
DESCRIPTION:Join us every Wednesday for a relaxed and creative life drawing session! Whether you’re a beginner or an experienced artist\, this group is open to everyone who wants to practice their drawing skills in a relaxed and supportive environment. Grab your sketchbook and pencils and come unleash your creativity with us! \n\n\n\nSessions are untutored and self directed. \n\n\n\nBoards and Easels are provided\, materials are not\, but you are welcome to bring anything you would like. There are sinks in the room for paint/ink/clay etc. \n\n\n\nPlease contact Sophie about any access requirements and she will do her best to accommodate you.
URL:https://tlchub.org.uk/event/life-drawing-wednesdays-2/2026-04-01/
LOCATION:Todmorden Learning Centre and Community Hub\, Todmorden Learning Centre and Community Hub\, Burnley Rd\, Todmorden\, OL14 7BX\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:Art and crafts
ORGANIZER;CN="Sophie Cleaver":MAILTO:sophie_cleaver@hotmail.co.uk
END:VEVENT
